程序包 starray.java.mono4j

类 MonoRuntime

java.lang.Object
starray.java.mono4j.MonoRuntime
public final class MonoRuntime extends Object
Mono 运行时信息和初始化管理类 Mono runtime information and initialization management class

提供运行时版本、架构、模式等信息的只读访问，同时提供类型转换辅助方法 Provides read-only access to runtime version, architecture, mode info, and type conversion helpers
